        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;@startuml\nactor User\nparticipant \&quot;Booking System\&quot; as System\ndatabase \&quot;Database\&quot; as DB\nparticipant \&quot;Payment Gateway\&quot; as Payment\nentity \&quot;Ticket\&quot; as Ticket\n\n== Movie Selection ==\nUser -&gt; System: select movie &amp; showtime\nactivate System\nSystem -&gt; DB: fetch available seats\nactivate DB\nDB --&gt; System: seat list\ndeactivate DB\nSystem --&gt; User: display available seats\ndeactivate System\n\n== Seat Selection ==\nUser -&gt; System: select preferred seats\nactivate System\nSystem -&gt; DB: validate seat availability\nactivate DB\nalt seats available\n  DB --&gt; System: seat confirmed\n  deactivate DB\n  System --&gt; User: seat selection confirmed\nelse seats unavailable\n  DB --&gt; System: seat not available\n  deactivate DB\n  System --&gt; User: error message\nend\ndeactivate System\n\n== Payment ==\nUser -&gt; System: enter payment details\nactivate System\nSystem -&gt; Payment: process payment\nactivate Payment\nalt payment successful\n  Payment --&gt; System: confirmation\n  deactivate Payment\n  System -&gt; DB: update booking record\n  activate DB\n  DB --&gt; System: booking saved\n  deactivate DB\n  System -&gt; Ticket: generate ticket\n  activate Ticket\n  Ticket --&gt; System: ticket object\n  deactivate Ticket\n  System --&gt; User: ticket sent\nelse payment failed\n  Payment --&gt; System: failure notice\n  deactivate Payment\n  System --&gt; User: payment error message\nend\ndeactivate System\n@enduml\n&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;format&quot;: &quot;svg&quot;&#xa;}" id="MKjcWziO7cRyFuyZaLJE-1">
